  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf ? \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd ? - \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bcb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Political debate in the party leader's meeting: Who is the president? Who is the Prime Minister? - Here are the full details",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe, Anurakumar Dissanayake and Sumandran participated in this meeting through virtual (Zoom).",
        "In this case, it was discussed in the party leader's meeting that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe should step down together and after that the Speaker should hold the position of Acting President for a short period of time.",
        "In addition, the party leader Maithripala Sirisena has insisted in the meeting that the President and the Prime Minister should resign.",
        "Meanwhile, the party leader Maithripala Sirisena also emphasized in the meeting that if the President and Prime Minister do not step down, the country will have to face serious consequences in the coming days.",
        "Meanwhile, independent party leaders expressed strong opposition to the idea of \u200b\u200bappointing Ranil Wickramasinghe as the interim president.",
        "In this case, Kota Go Home is against President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and No Deal is against Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe. If Ranil Wickremesinghe is appointed as the President, the people will destroy the Parliament, party leader Vasudeva Nanayakkara said in the meeting.",
        "Meanwhile, the Prime Minister did not agree to the resignation of the Prime Minister and the President, despite the party leader's meeting demanding his resignation. However, Raub Hakeem said that the decision has been taken to request the resignation of both the President and the Prime Minister due to the request of many people."
      ],
